Class AlertConfigImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.AlertConfigImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, AlertConfig, Storable
public class AlertConfigImpl extends BaseObjectImpl implements AlertConfig
Alert Configuration object server-side implementation. Connects a particular alert type ("event" field) to a number of sign group/message pattern pairs to control which signs are eligible for inclusion in an alert and which message template to use.
Author:
Gordon Parikh, Douglas Lau
